{"tid":1474301,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"扮記者 必須＿","createTime":"2019-08-15T06:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:19:06.000Z","uid":169262,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a48122557984e5fd24eab8e66fe20e6a24e8efe8","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:31:50.000Z","msg":"相中人並非Now新聞台及製作部嘅攝影師，而此人身上所穿著橙色背心經同事查證係2016七人欖球賽時發予製作公司用作拍攝球賽之用。相中人穿著此背心多次在示威現場出現拍攝，未能知道此人拍攝嘅意圖及用途。希望各位行家見到相中人的話可聯絡小弟或Now新聞部同事處理.<br />\n<br />\n歡迎及麻煩各行家幫忙轉載🙏🏽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdsLJyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdsLJyn.jpg&h=5a61d9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5um1j2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5um1j2.jpg&h=725b5c69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64c4d01c1a35cb5de3d4ecb6b961368a3f9e556c","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:21.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"33ee15b5ff5c9139930426b8cb4be4298522ae05","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"978a33e1735032efc9f6db0eabf9570377f986f4","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:41.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"1512e4110e9c23c903e7bdb6cd93c234738091a6","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:32:52.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"682b80ef8ccd5d7925d68f9c3b42bea50155c48c","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:02.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"4ed62db91efd9b4c0c07bb62236135867ec9ed20","tid":1474301,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:33:14.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"e063fdc0d7491ddc75d741f35c8aaef9d311b07a","tid":1474301,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl